<TITLE>'Celebrate exams like festivals'</TITLE>


<TEXT>
New Delhi: Prime Minister Narendra Modi <EVENT eid="e1" class="OCCURRENCE">dedicated</EVENT> his first radio address of the <TIMEX3 tid="t1" type="DURATION" value="PXY">New Year</TIMEX3> -- Mann ki Baat -- to students, <EVENT eid="e2" class="REPORTING">telling</EVENT> them that exams can <EVENT eid="e3" class="OCCURRENCE">bring</EVENT> out the best in them only when they are "celebrated as festivals". 
        
