"A happy mind is the secret for a good mark sheet," the Prime Minister <EVENT eid="e4" class="REPORTING">said</EVENT>. When a student is <EVENT eid="e5" class="STATE">under</EVENT> tension, knowledge <EVENT eid="e6" class="OCCURRENCE">takes</EVENT> a back seat. "Do not <EVENT eid="e7" class="REPORTING">let</EVENT> that happen," he <EVENT eid="e8" class="REPORTING">told</EVENT> students. 
 
It is important to <EVENT eid="e9" class="OCCURRENCE">study</EVENT> to <EVENT eid="e10" class="OCCURRENCE">gain</EVENT> knowledge and not marks, he <EVENT eid="e11" class="REPORTING">said</EVENT>. For a student, <EVENT eid="e12" class="OCCURRENCE">studying</EVENT> for marks is <EVENT eid="e13" class="OCCURRENCE">limiting</EVENT>. "It is important to <EVENT eid="e14" class="OCCURRENCE">study</EVENT> for knowledge," he <EVENT eid="e15" class="REPORTING">added</EVENT>. 
 
To the parents, he <EVENT eid="e16" class="REPORTING">said</EVENT>, "I <EVENT eid="e17" class="I_ACTION">urge</EVENT> parents to <EVENT eid="e18" class="OCCURRENCE">accept</EVENT> rather than <EVENT eid="e19" class="OCCURRENCE">expect</EVENT>. Our expectations from our children should not <EVENT eid="e20" class="OCCURRENCE">get</EVENT> heavy". 
 
In view of the coming assembly elections in five states, the government had <EVENT eid="e21" class="OCCURRENCE">approached</EVENT> the Election Commission seeking clearance for the programme as the Model Code of Conduct is in force in the five states. Uttar Pradesh, Punjab, Goa, Uttarakhand and Manipur go to polls between <TIMEX3 tid="t2" type="DATE" value="2017-02-04">February 4</TIMEX3> and <TIMEX3 tid="t3" type="DATE" value="2017-03-08">March 8</TIMEX3>. The results will be <EVENT eid="e22" class="OCCURRENCE">declared</EVENT> on <TIMEX3 tid="t4" type="DATE" value="2017-03-11">March 11</TIMEX3>. 
 
The board exams <EVENT eid="e23" class="ASPECTUAL">begin</EVENT> on <TIMEX3 tid="t5" type="DATE" value="2017-03-09">March 9</TIMEX3> -- <TIMEX3 tid="t6" type="DURATION" value="P1D">a day</TIMEX3> after the assembly elections end.
</TEXT>


